title: How to sign in and out of my online account - Sam's Club
snippet: If you are not yet a Sam's Club Member, join now Can't remember your password, reset your password now To Sign out: Highlight the Sign In / Account dropdown right of the Search bar and select Sign Out at the bottom of the account options.

title: Benefits of Club & Plus Membership - Sam's Club
snippet: Free Delivery from Club: Plus members receive free select same-day or next-day free delivery from your local club on eligible orders over $50 ($12 fee for Club members). Early Shopping Hours: Plus members can shop up to an hour early in-club & avoid the crowds, select exclusions apply. See Sam's Club Hours.

title: Create a new Sam's Club Membership
snippet: Create a new Sam's Club Membership Select the Join Sam's Club link at the bottom of any SamsClub.com page to compare the benefits of a Club ($50) or Plus ($110) Membership and instantly create a new membership. Complete all required fields; fields with a * must be completed.
